we grew up with a 63 bus and then a 65 bus until my dad got an American van
in 1969. In both cases he extended the seatbelts with hand bent steel
straps. The center portions of my SC seat belts are also extended with 8"
steel 1/8" steel straps attached to the original mounting points in the
wheel well. My wife and I needed the, um, extra room. heh heh

